Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:21.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:35.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:47.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:57.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:10.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:14.83,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:23.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:27.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年才刚过完没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青少年们就开始失控浮躁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,客人,客人 你是怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对喔,明天就是第一次共通考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#03 暗夜中心跳不已 和响子单独相处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考生真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要对五代多关心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正是最后的紧要关头 他一定紧张得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丑喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次共通考试 明天终于要登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自信吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,有自信我就不会烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这一年 就应该更努力用功一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都还没做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都没做吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,连手都还没牵到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么 当然是管理员的事罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在什么都还没做…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞争对手又少了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去跟四谷和朱美他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请他们不要吵五代念书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先从朱美开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊?有什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,出了什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事,请快点过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,快点过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你是怎么了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这么少当然会冷罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样的话 你铁定会重考第二次喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶,重考第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,你找我有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天五代要参加第一次共通考试 我想告诉你不要刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要穿得这么清凉 在公寓里走来走去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我刚才想对你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!不准看!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你不在家吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,四谷不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快趁现在来个总复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜我是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷出现了,四谷出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜对了,你怎么会知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,原来你在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么时候来的? 从哪里进来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从刚刚一直就在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于我是怎么进来的嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(秘密)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又挖了一个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子的秘密通道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,你立刻离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你好冷漠喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,今天对五代而言 是非常重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以再对他恶作剧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶好耶,终于进入状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛打我?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼去外面玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,这个走廊最好滑了 (“滑”音同“落榜”)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你居然说了我最忌讳的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被重考生打了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这么一句话吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没有别的话说了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐吧,汁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人明天要考试 脾气难免大了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重考生就可以为所欲为吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以打弱小的小孩吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等考完试再加倍奉还就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.05,0:09:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面子,你一定要等我到考试通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等不了那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个社会 都对重考生那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊溜滑板有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑板不能滑的话 还有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说说话啊,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能说“滑”这个字!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑!滑!我想要溜滑板!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要溜滑板,我想要溜滑板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤太郎,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之进屋里去就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要,我不要进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬天的…雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会变成泪雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天没有念到的部分 要一口气追回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把我的房间当作宴会厅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里早就变成宴会厅了 有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干嘛?你来干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈,你不是说考试要到了 不可以吵重考生吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦,他已经变成 没听到宴会吵闹声就无法念书了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正明天他一定会很沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要好好地疯一疯 让他壮烈地成仁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你们又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我郑重地再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试的季节就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请暂时不要去吵五代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五代面前绝对不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考 之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连开玩笑都不能喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说不能说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你大声一点再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.47,0:13:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落、滑倒、第二次重考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出去吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我要去朋友家念书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这实在太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能办得到!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你一定办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,这是什么烂环境
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋…鞋带断掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吉祥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经超越了 “不吉祥”这个字能形容的范围了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要气馁,明年还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用这种奇怪的话安慰我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说 四谷说得没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊 明年考不上的话,还有后年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位,你们不要太过份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我真的要生气罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛气成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她从白天就一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 管理员对重考生有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不出面的话 你们一定会没完没了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敷衍、欺骗、前后不一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员的脸变红了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为五代着想而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变主意不出门了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.31,0:15:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了回报你的一片真心 我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全认真起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还真乐观啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员对我有所期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们这一栋停电耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是保险丝烧断了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你要念书…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停电怎么念书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪,保险丝没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是配线出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话,先看看配线图吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会修吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会,且工具都很齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对维修也略懂一二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在这里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:16:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次来这个阁楼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处在暗室里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这里是个钟塔小屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,那个坏掉的时钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有种古老图书馆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像古董店的店头摆饰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刻馆的历史真的很悠久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么时候建的呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了,青春的一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昭和15年(1940年)3月13日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待再相逢 昭和19年(1944年)10月17日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在战争期间写的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个时代 爱上一个人一定很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争不晓得拆散了多少对情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们活着的这个时代 真是和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是以前住在这里的人 已经变成回忆的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是一刻馆的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我会喜欢上一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给小樱 昭和19年(1944年),一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一段没有结局的爱情吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心看出神了,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点把停电修好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我得努力把它修好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为明天是你的重要日子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员 什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为了我这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是为了你着想,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒啊,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说你们一直没回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,来吧 不用在意我们,请继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在胡说些什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惣一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在对她养的狗道歉耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她刚才摔倒的时候 好像有撞到头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一只老鼠烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是它咬断了电线啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来修
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是时钟的声音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个时钟早就坏掉了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理应坏了的钟塔时钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得为什么突然响了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.62,0:22:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的钟声,在下着雨的城镇中 整夜响个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.57,0:23:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正整晚都没睡 顺便出来送你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会再开宴会安慰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力而为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.01,0:23:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他滑得还真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.87,0:23:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话已经持续说了一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.94,0:23:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.77,0:23:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是迟迟没有上榜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.34,0:24:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回 ‘响子紧张万分?五代考试中’
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事? 他居然从考场逃了出来?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要陪他去应考
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:06.25,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.41,0:24:35.69,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}为何你能如此若无其事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:43.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}光只是眨个眼 就能让我悸动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:51.62,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}使我身陷险境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:25:06.30,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}明明已经可以相爱 偏偏时机还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:18.56,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}我快要忍受不了 快要变成了愚蠢的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.60,0:25:23.94,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}真是痛苦的折磨

